docstring: """Database functions that do comparisons or type conversions."""

classes.docstring: """Coerce an expression to a new field type."""
classes.name: Cast

classes.docstring: """Return, from left to right, the first non-null expression."""
classes.name: Coalesce

classes.docstring:
"""
    Return the maximum expression.

    If any expression is null the return value is database-specific:
    On PostgreSQL, the maximum not-null expression is returned.
    On MySQL, Oracle, and SQLite, if any expression is null, null is returned.
    """
classes.name: Greatest

classes.docstring:
"""
    Return the minimum expression.

    If any expression is null the return value is database-specific:
    On PostgreSQL, return the minimum not-null expression.
    On MySQL, Oracle, and SQLite, if any expression is null, return null.
    """
classes.name: Least
